    <note>Fan(2) Lingsun [7025] His family was originally from Daming and his grandson, Shou [16796], was buried in Qingzhou, Yidu. Based on generational name and Liu Ban, WJ, 39.2b, Lingsun is a grandson of Zhi [8041] and probably son of Min [577] (may be nephew). He was Wang(2) Dan's [8153] son-in-law. His great grandson, based on generational name and address, Fan(2) Shiji [3285], was Cai(1) Chengxi's [1645] son-in-law. Zhao Dingchen, WJ, 18.7b-9b (funerary inscription of Shide [3271], probable brother of Shiji).</note>
